{"type":null,"faqId":38999,"title":"表带脏了如何清洁？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:18.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">当您的表带脏了的时候，建议您可以使用沾水的纸巾或湿布擦拭、清洁表带，在清洁的时候请注意：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\n\"><span>1.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">请勿使用烈性化学制品、清洗剂或强洗涤剂清洁设备或其配件，避免对表带或表盘造成腐蚀和损伤。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\n\"><span>2.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">清洁和维护前，请注意断开手环和充电器的连接。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\n\"><span>3.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">手环具有</span><span style=\"line-height:\n150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">IP68</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">级防尘防水，能够满足大家的日常使用，但是依然有可能避免不了水汽侵袭，所以清洁后请使用干布或干纸巾彻底擦干并放置足够长的时间，以避免残余水汽在手环内部凝结，造成机体伤害。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4309","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673017000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":64,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}